        <updateDate>2020-07-01T17:58:01Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Essential Pay for Essential Workers Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires employers to pay essential health care employees a premium amount in addition to their regular rate of pay during an emergency period. It also allows employers a payroll tax credit for the payment of such enhanced wages to essential employees. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
